ریاضی
لگاریتم
لگاریتم e (ln)
log(x,a) = 1/log(a,x)
log(x,a) = log(x,10)/log(a,10)
secx = 1/cosx
cscx = 1/sinx
1+tg^2x = sec^2x
1+cotg^2x = csc^2x
sin(a+-b) = sina*cosb +- cosa*sinb
cos(a+-b) = cosa*cosb -+ sina*sinb
توابع هایپربولیک (هذلولی)
x^2 - y^2 = 1
coshx^2 - sinhx^2 = 1
tghx = sinhx / coshx
cothx = coshx / sinhx
sinhx = (e^x - e^-x)/2
coshx = (e^x + e^-x)/2
tghx = (e^x - e^-x)/(e^x + e^-x)
cotghx = (e^x + e^-x)/(e^x - e^-x)
cschx = 2/(e^x - e^-x) 
sechx = 2/(e^x + e^-x) 
sinh(a+-b) = sinha*coshb +- cosha*sinb
cosh(a+-b) = cosha*coshb +- sinha*sinhb
tgh(u+-v) = (tghu +- tghu) / (1+-tghu*tghv)
tghu * cotgh = 1
sechu = 1/coshu
cschu = 1/sinhu
