[Image 51.jpg]
قوانین حد:
\lxa = lim(x->a)
\lxa f(x) = \Lone
\lxa g(x) = \Ltwo
f(x) = c
=> \Lone = c
\lxa cf(x) = c.\Lone
\lxa cf(x) +- bg(x) = c\Lone +- b\Ltwo
\lxa f(x).g(x) = \Lone.\Ltwo
\lxa f(x)/g(x) = \Lone/\Ltwo
\lxa | f(x) | = | \Lone |
\lxa rad(n, f(x)) = rad(n, \Lone)
if n=2k <=> \Lone >= 0

\lxa f(x)^n = \Lone^n

